data.description: Beautifully  updated & upgraded is this very well maintained & meticulously clean Home which shows better in person than in pictures. Great move-in condition. Located in a quiet neighborhood in Brandywine Hundred.  It has a nice open floor lay-out both on main & upper levels & plenty of natural light throughout.  Features: gleaming hardwood floors in the living rm and kitchen, new carpets, fresh paint, kitchen w/ stainless appliances (smart fridge & smart electric range can both be remotely accessed by cellphone & the range has built-in air fryer),  granite countertops, backsplash & a breakfast nook. Stainless front loading washer & dryer & exhaust fan in laundry rm.  Additional features: bay windows in living & dining rms, newer windows, free standing electric fireplace,  new chandelier  in the formal dining rm, 4 ceiling fan/lamps,  roof deck off the master bdrm, wrap-around wrought iron fence in the spacious front & side yards, backyard w/ vinyl privacy fence and nice size deck, a spacious storage shed w/ 2 windows and an oversized garage w/ door to backyard and side window.  The driveway can park 4 vehicles. Additional updates include:  All new roof (2022),  newer windows, new electrical lines for large appliances, newer hvac, newer hot water heater. Utilities include: natural gas for heat & hot water heater.  The home has built-in security system including a video/audio recording doorbell by front door. No deed restrictions in the neighborhood & the annual HOA dues are voluntary. Located close to major shopping centers & less than a mile away from 95 north/south …Easy Access to 495, 1.5 Miles to the Train Station and 16 miles to the Philadelphia International Airport. This meticulously kept Home is “Immediately available” for the New Homeowner. Just move right in. NOTE: there are hardwood floors underneath the new carpets throughout the home including the staircase. Located on the corner of a less busy secondary road but amazingly the vehicle sounds are muffled and does not disturb the quiet atmosphere inside this home. (do not be fooled by the age of this home… it is very contemporary inside and out (built w/ classic building methods that withstand the test of time.)  Truly a pleasure to show. (Previously listed for $425k) ..NOTE: the 🏠 does not have a basement but plenty of storage space in the new Shed which is by the driveway. New homeowner has the option to use the oversized garage as storage space.
